WEBINAR ACCESS INFORMATION

PREPAY FOR YOUR 2022 ANNUAL PASS or PREPAY FOR THIS JANUARY 15 WEBINAR MEETING ONLY
Here is your opportunity to give a $135 donation and secure an “annual pass” for 2022.  This includes 10 meetings, 5 Webinars, and 5 that are both Webinars and in person at the Skirball Cultural Center.  Please note that meetings will alternate between Webinar ONLY, and Skirball/Webinar Combo events. You may also prepay $10 for the Webinar ONLY event.
THIS PURCHASE SITE WILL CLOSE ON FRIDAY, JANUARY 14 AT 6 PM.
 
CLICK HERE TO GET YOUR ANNUAL PASS FOR 2022 or PREPAY FOR WEBINAR MEETING ONLY
Note: (1) A Webinar registration link for this event will be emailed to payees on two dates: January 7 in the early evening, and January 14 after this purchase site closes at 6 pm; (2) Annual pass holders will receive a "name tag pass" at the Skirball Cultural Center at each of the 5 Skirball meetings next year, and will also receive an email with the registration link for all 10 Webinar meetings.  You will have the choice of viewing the Webinar on screen or attending the Skirball Center in person. Your annual pass gives you access to Skirball or the Webinar for each of the five combo Skirball/Webinar events.
